<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About us</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/styles.css"> -->
    <style>
        /* General styling for the main content */
        .about-main {
            padding: 80px 0;
                  background: linear-gradient(to right, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
            /* background-color: #f4f7f9; */
            color: #34495e;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 60px); /* Adjust based on header height */
        }
        
        .about-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .about-heading {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ecf0f1;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-paragraph {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* You can use this for a call-to-action button or link if needed */
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .head{
                  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- This EJS tag includes the header partial file -->
    <div class="head"><%- include("partials/header.ejs") %></div>

    <main class="about-main">
        <div class="about-container">
            <h1 class="about-heading">About Skill Wrap</h1>
            
            <p class="about-paragraph">
                Skill Wrap is a platform designed to help you organize and showcase your work. 
                Whether you are a freelancer, a student, or a professional, our tools are built to streamline your workflow and present your skills in the best light.
            </p>
            
            <p class="about-paragraph">
                Our mission is to empower individuals by providing a seamless experience for managing projects, collaborating with others, and building a strong professional portfolio. We believe that your work deserves to be seen, and our platform makes that a reality.
            </p>
            
            <a href="/dashboard" class="cta-button">Explore the Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>